title: #60 - JHBTeam on Being Called the Next Karl Jacobs & Meeting Lil Nas X
itunes:title: #60 - JHBTeam on Being Called the Next Karl Jacobs & Meeting Lil Nas X
description: On this CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, 100 Thieves Senior Intern JHBTeam comes on as a guest to talk about his meteoric rise as a fan of 100 Thieves to content creator. They cover a range of topics such as JHB getting blocked by Drake Bell on Twitter, calling out to Lil Nas X to come on TBH with JHB, playing Minecraft with Amouranth, collabing with Pokimane, JHB's most regrettable tweet, and more!
